          <p class="hero-copy">Log in to access the XeonDB Cloud Dashboard and manage your databases in one place: create
            clusters, control access, and monitor performance.</p>
          <div class="hero-points" aria-label="Notes">
            <div class="hero-point">
              <strong>Cloud dashboard</strong>
              <span>Provision clusters, manage keyspaces and tables, and rotate credentials.</span>
